OL,3,CPay offer would see new teachers start
OL,4,Con #30k
OL,6,FThe education minister has outlined
OL,7,Fthe details of a new pay offer for
OL,8,Fteachers in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FPaul Givan says the proposals would
OL,11,Fsee the starting salary for teachers
OL,12,Frise to #30,000, which represents a
OL,13,F24.3% rise and brings the starting
OL,14,Fpoint in line with England.
OL,16,FHe says the offer equates to a
OL,17,Fcumulative total of 10.4% plus #1,000
OL,18,Fbeing applied to the other teachers'
OL,19,Fand leadership pay scales.
