OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers' Council
OL,7,Fsays the proposal represents "a
OL,8,Fsignificant increase to the starting
OL,9,Fsalary for teachers and an uplift in
OL,10,Fteachers' and school leaders pay from
OL,11,F1 September 2023".
OL,13,FThe union says it has agreed to
OL,14,Fconsult members in the coming week,
OL,15,F"with a view to responding to the
OL,16,Foffer by 26 March".
OL,18,FMr Givan says he hopes the offer will
OL,19,Fbring to an end industrial action and
OL,20,Fstabilise the system.
