OL,6,FThe education minister said it was
OL,7,Funacceptable that teachers have been
OL,8,Fwaiting three years for a pay increase.
OL,10,F"I am pleased that there has been
OL,11,Fsignificant progress on the issue of
OL,12,Fthe teachers' pay with a formal offer
OL,13,Fbeing made to the teaching unions," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"This offer, which equates to a 24.3%
OL,17,Fpay rise for beginning teachers, will
OL,18,Fhelp both attract and retain the best
OL,19,Fteachers to our schools.
