OL,6,F"It is unacceptable that teachers have
OL,7,Fbeen waiting three years for a pay
OL,8,Fincrease. I have made it clear that my
OL,9,Fhighest priority is to ensure that the
OL,10,Fteaching profession is paid at a rate
OL,11,Fwhich recognises the value of their
OL,12,Fprofession.
OL,14,F"This is a positive step in that
OL,15,Fdirection, and I commend the positive
OL,16,Fnegotiations that have taken place
OL,17,Fwithin the Teachers' Negotiating
OL,18,FCommittee (TNC) which consists of
OL,19,Fmanagement and the trade unions
OL,20,Frepresenting teachers and school
OL,21,Fleaders."
