OL,6,FThe five teaching unions which make up
OL,7,Fthe Northern Ireland Teaching Council
OL,8,F(NITC) are set to consult with their
OL,9,Fmembers on the proposals.
OL,11,FMr Givan said he urged teachers and
OL,12,Fschool leaders to consider the formal
OL,13,Foffer, adding if accepted and
OL,14,Fimplemented, it will "bring an end to
OL,15,Fall industrial action which has been
OL,16,Fongoing since May 2022".
